Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/brendonreed/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    on windows
    git clone git://github.com/brendonreed/dotvim.git ~/vimfiles

Create symlinks or set pointer :

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

in windows download and use Junction from sysinternals:
    junction vimfiles c:\Users\breed\vimfiles
and for the VsVim extension, from  home directore (c:\Users\breed):
    mklink _vsvimrc vimfiles\vsvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    
